      "text": "Microphone -> Audio Capture -> Speech to Text -> Intent -> Business Logic -> Text to Speech -> Speaker\n\n   ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Microphone -> Audio Capture -> Speech to Text -> Intent -> Business Logic -> Text to Speech -> Speaker\n\n   ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FI63gTlUoLe49OvN9hvX5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -221,
      "y": 518,
      "width": 734.3995361328125,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1568559309,
      "version": 391,
      "versionNonce": 1587560589,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781321397159,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Major Steps of STT:\n1. Audio Capture -> Microphone records the sound waves\n2. Preprocessing -> Noise removal, Volume Normalization\n3. Feature Extraction - > NUmerical format ( MFCC)\n4. Recognization -> Deep Neural Network Converts them back to the words\n5. Post processing -> Formatting, Punctuation, other NLP process",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Major Steps of STT:\n1. Audio Capture -> Microphone records the sound waves\n2. Preprocessing -> Noise removal, Volume Normalization\n3. Feature Extraction - > NUmerical format ( MFCC)\n4. Recognization -> Deep Neural Network Converts them back to the words\n5. Post processing -> Formatting, Punctuation, other NLP process",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Bkdw2kuKwA29jUlAbjFfK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -222,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 888.2994384765625,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
